{
  "stem": "11916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they was promised by the German, they're not going to kill them, because they was working with them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not in their heart, they just want to save their life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they arrive in Auschwitz about-- no, in Reichenbach-- about two weeks before Christmas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when we asked them what did happen in Auschwitz, they told us for the last three months, Auschwitz was burning and never, ever stop.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they burn everyone whom they could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think, finally, the Russian was so very close, they have to close Auschwitz somehow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this how about this eight or 10 girls was taken to Reichenbach.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They was all Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we have no sorrow to the Germans this time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "All we was wishing to get all they deserve.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I feel much better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very hungry, but somehow I was hoping to survive, and I try to work for this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know one survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other, we kind of-- you know, quite often, we was separated in the wagons, and I don't know whether they do survive or not.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Christmas Day, the bomb was coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't get the bomb when the Jews was working, though the other side, which get the bomb, was also all people who was working, wasn't German.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They was the same, but maybe wasn't Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some German was working, also, in this factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most of the one who was working there, they came back from the war amputated with one legs, maybe even both of their legs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they put them back to work, whatever they can do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The bomb fall just about where we were, but still not over our head, but maybe to the next and the next building.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
